Title: The Quantisation of Charges
Authors: David I Olive
Comments: 9 pages, no figures, invited conference talk
Report-no: SWAT/00/278
\\
  The question as to whether the integrality of the spectrum of observed
electric charges is due to a quantum effext has fascinated theoretical
physicists throughout the last century. It leads to unanswered questions at the
heart of quantum field theory and its role as a framework for particle physics.
